use a slide rule, how to use a slide rule so that they

12:29.686 --> 12:48.132
could compete effectively and learn in a 
classroom environment. That's one of the

12:48.152 --> 12:52.198
interesting experiences about my first year 
there. I can understand Rod making the decision

12:52.218 --> 12:57.465
not to, allow the four or five kids or 10 kids who had 
calculators to use them. Uh, but for him to take the

13:04.078 --> 13:28.228
