those kids who did not have knowledge of the slide

13:04.078 --> 13:28.228
rule use so that they could could compete 
effectively and learn in the, in that, in that

13:04.078 --> 13:28.228
learning environment, uh, I think is a great 
attestation to the nature of the relationships

13:04.078 --> 13:28.228
