13:39.163 --> 13:49.872
classes, for example. But that extra effort, I 
think, on Ron's part was indicative of the

13:50.113 --> 13:58.300
pretty much across the board attitude of faculty 
in terms of their relationship with students and

13:58.735 --> 14:17.702
that I think is a great compliment and that is 
something that I hope will never be lost in the

13:58.735 --> 14:17.702
learning environment at Texas A&M. One year later 
